FBIS4-18840 "drweu069_i_94011" FBIS-WEU-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 FRANCE Dassault AT To Supply PRC Telephone System Dassault AT To Supply PRC Telephone System AU0804170994 Paris AFP in English 1430 GMT 8 Apr 94 AU0804170994 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Paris, April 8 (AFP) -- French firm Dassault Automatismes et Telecommunications (of the Dassault Electronique Group) on Friday [8 April] announced signature of a contract for supplying a complete wireless digital telephony system for the city of Chongqing, in Sichuan Province, southwestern China. It did not indicate the value of the contract. The announcement indicated that the network for Chongqing will be the equivalent of the French "Bi-Bop" cordless telephone, used by some pedestrians in Paris and other areas to make calls from wherever they happen to be.
